{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/zoomlevel"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)zoomLevel","title":"zoomLevel","symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"}],"fragments":[{"text":"zoomLevel","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"double","preciseIdentifier":"c:d","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"zoomLevel"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition to affecting the visual size and detail of features on the map,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the zoom level affects the size of the vector tiles that are loaded. At zoom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"level 0, each tile covers the entire world map; at zoom level 1, it covers ¼","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the world; at zoom level 2, "},{"type":"text","text":"1"},{"text":"⁄","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"16"},{"type":"text","text":" of the world, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so on."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setZoomLevel:animated:"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"ident